  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "動物を育てながらペットショップを経営し、祖母の病気を治すための薬草を探し、店舗を繁盛させるためのさまざまな依頼をこなすRPGです。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Kawaii Pet Shop Monogatari is an RPG where you manage a pet shop, raise animals, participate in competitions, and travel for events. Complete various requests to improve your shop's reputation.\n\nThe protagonist's grandmother, who runs a pet shop, falls ill and is hospitalized. In her place, the protagonist takes over managing the pet shop and sets off on an adventure with excellent pets to find ingredients for a medicine to cure the illness.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
